{"tid":2279464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國財政部宣布制裁劉賜蕙、李桂華、鄧中華及李江舟","createTime":"2020-11-09T22:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T03:56:12.000Z","uid":133159,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c730b7200ff472555d7ff6e9e74a80e71268a72f","tid":2279464,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T22:16:16.000Z","msg":"美國財政部宣布因應香港的情況，對另外4人實施制裁，以示不滿壓制香港特區的不同政見人士。被制裁的4人，包括警務處國家安全處副處長劉賜蕙、警務處國家安全處高級警司李桂華、港澳辦副主任鄧中華，以及中央政府駐港國安公署副署長李江舟。美國財政部在網站，公開4人的個人資料。美國政府早前已經就中國政府對香港實施《國家安全法》等，暫停與香港特區的引渡條約、取消香港的特殊待遇，亦宣布制裁行政長官林鄭月娥、多名特區高級官員及相關人士。<br />\n<br />\n2020-11-10 03:18:51 (1)"},{"pid":"3b691d491b3d45829719a24bab2dff5bfe296f0b","tid":2279464,"uid":392,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T22:24:43.000Z","msg":"馬戲華<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c1e0034ed5982c360578fa0d5efd4997be1a33","tid":2279464,"uid":261937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b691d491b3d45829719a24bab2dff5bfe296f0b","tid":2279464,"uid":392,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T22:24:43.000Z","msg":"馬戲華<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T22:26:04.000Z","msg":"congratulations"},{"pid":"ae3da2be2bb035866b34e7c04fc80587071f5018","tid":2279464,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T22:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e736a33c54a557e91cdbf4bbfe2bb95e59a9dd5b","tid":2279464,"uid":34377,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T22:28:34.000Z",